 src=\"img/uploads/20190306125128ui3SsQfhP7wMInEY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/miu-miu/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Miu Miu 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>本季系列中，玛丽珍鞋、手提包和系带高筒马丁靴成为少女装扮中最重要的亮点。A 字廓形大衣、透明印花连衣裙、迷彩飞行员夹克和短袖针织衫则将少女气质细分为不同类型，供顾客各取所需：朋克的、柔美的、高贵的、休闲的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125302NpmIn8iZa3HqSV2B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125302lPr5m7QhXKq1829x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125303Ea3x6FfKX7l08osV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125303kJjctp4MXKhLsvR5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125304XsfpYogyAFaIK0tw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125304Bgchx30Y2yjJAE4q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125304RZL3npIh5Fc6l7Q1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125304mF3VIdfHQGpA2wXg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125305TmgJQG6EVRBWOv8i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030612530545kWDKwfxpF2BaHs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125305FnLJtSNYG3Uw8KzH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125305jPw1LCTQmN9gicu5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125306oHhkGP2wfyC8Wztq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030612530649brAyBTPSY1Rwsh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125306ml3ErfFU9Cat06JY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125306Bj53a0KYZXEtn6pr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125306O1M3NquPAKXmZygE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125307fb27u9XxAEM3RnVr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125308Mu3hcLvA9jKmyG87.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125307ML5bZ97k1QKxop3v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125308bp1cLMYr2ytFfAwx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125308ThP3rcxeX1K9HVWE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903061253090MPqkDEpmHasRGir.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125309zTuSQc3lnOBXHo4P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125310C39IGwhNWBl7EurZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125310HQBr4gZA5EYXeTvJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125310CVwBqtQ461c9rWjd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/lacoste/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lacoste 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>这是新任创意总监 Louise Trotter 上任以来的首个系列。第一套 look 被称为“the&nbsp;René coat”，致敬创始人设计的双排扣风衣，领布内侧为绿色缝线装饰，人字纹内饰则是取自 Lacoste 设计的第一双网球鞋。<br></p><p>整个系列并不会让人感到怀旧和复古，相反， Louise Trotter 为了让“Lacoste”更时髦加入了不少细节：衬衫领的设计减少了运动衫套装的休闲感，外搭风衣、针织大背心等能直接提升造型感；撞色设计带来了丰富性；运动面料和针织面料的拼接也让整套 look 更富于变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125440cbKfrNsto0RhyvBU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903061254415Y8lDV7FETgtrsOC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125442rSc2qe6nMOpftsQN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125446BRKQjV1xsD2FpC9M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125441JKENmHscIuW16ZAy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125441oj9fEwDMXCclI5Ft.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125442Mw5HYJKjOevNraZI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190306125442ws6JayNZEnu0IHBM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-form